      <prop type="x-translation-ref">株林.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>胡為乎株林？從夏南。匪適株林，從夏南。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What does he in Zhulin?
He is going after Xianan.
He is not going to Zhulin;
He is going after Xianan.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
