      <prop type="x-translation-ref">株林.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>駕我乘馬，說于株野。乘我乘駒，朝食于株。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>' Yoke for me my team of horses;
I will rest in the country about Zhu.
I will drive my team of colts,
And breakfast at Zhu.'</seg>
      </tuv>
